descriptionHtml:
As promised,here\'s my savegame of my main Char Nefehya.
Shes lvl 1,dark elf,more warrior type.Of course you can make her a hunter or mage to,it\'s in your hands (:
Shes pretty much at the beginning,you have to travel to Whiterun now.
!!!Feel free to make screenshots with her!!!

How to install?
Copy into: ...\\my documents\\my games\\skyrim\\saves.
And you\'re done (:

Requirements: 
Badass Warpaint V1-1
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3377&navtag=file/images.php?id=3377&tab=3

ApachiiSkyHair (okay you don\'t necessarily need that,just if you want her cool dreads so its hightly recommended!)
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10168

HIGHLY recommended:
Coverwomen:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563

Covereyes:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=4869

CBBE:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666


Hope you will have fun with her!
author: xXBabyDreXx
